# Assets Insurance Loans Premium Funding Impairment Amount

## identifier
de8628

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of provisions for impairment in relation to loans provided to an insured for the purposes of funding their premium.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Assets.Insurance.LoansPremiumFundingImpairment.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.05
- period=instant
